https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/5uaXSJBa6rCgRqRFrfhgVycU9Sl.jpg In response to Morgan Spurlock's COMIC-CON: A FAN'S HOPE, comedian Doug Benson (SUPER HIGH ME) stars in this doc that looks at San Diego Comic-Con from his hazy perspective.
